cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.GR 

This paper is about object detection using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of synthetic datasets and domain randomization also involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the application of object detection has relevance to robotics (cs.RO) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories.
